CAContentCore - Class in service.tut.pori.contentanalysis
This class includes functions for general content operations, such as updating the keywords, modifying photo details, and uploading new content Note: this does not have UserEventListener for user removal, this is because currently all content is managed by ContentStorage service, which will call all the necessary method for removing photo content (when needed)
